Water_Temperature: Average water temperature, sampled at 1-minute intervals and averaged over 15 minutes.
Specific_Conductance: Average specific conductance, sampled at 1-minute intervals and averaged over 15 minutes.
Salinity: Average salinity, sampled at 1-minute intervals and averaged over 15 minutes.
Depth: Average water depth, sampled at 1-minute intervals and averaged over 15 minutes.
TDS: Average Total Dissolved Solids, sampled at 1-minute intervals and averaged over 15 minutes.
NAVD88_Depth: Water level relative to NAVD88, calculated with Matlab minus function and surveying on site
Depth_ft: Water level in feet, calculated with Matlab times function
NAVD88_Depth_ft: Water level in feet relative to NAVD88, calculated with Matlab times function and surveying on site
